{
  "stem": "8784.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was not the headquarters where Amon Goth would've been, but this was where the guards would have been.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And if I remember, the name of the guard there was Hujar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he was in charge.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "When we arrived, he got a hold of this fellow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The other fellow that came with me was by the name of Orbach, with an O-- spelled with an O.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there is a good chance that they wanted him and not me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But we will never know that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But as soon as we arrived there at this quarter of the guards-- these were mostly volunteers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "These were not Germans, but volunteer guards-- Lithuanians, Poles, possibly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And as soon as we arrived there, they took this fellow Orbach into the second room and began to torture him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I was sitting in this room observing what was going on in the other room where he was being tortured.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He was beaten.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He was-- when he was unconscious they dumped water on him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was able to see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not able to hear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was able to see because there was a glass door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was able to see that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw even the man being hung by the, with his hands tied to the back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was hung on those hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when he was turning blue or he was going unconscious, they would lower those ropes and he would fall to the floor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would dump water on him again, and the torture would continue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was only after some-- you know, if I had to judge time, it seemed like hours, but most likely it was minutes that they-- he was tortured.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after a short while, somebody came running in.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
